node.text:
Coming Up In This Industry I Would Reach Out To Designers or Brands I Looked Up To With No Replies Or They Would Give Me The Run Around. I’ve Been Wanting To Use My Platform & Collab With Up & Coming Designers Since Then. Even If They Have A Following Already, I Learned That A Simple Co Sign Can Go A Long Way. With That Being Said, In Collaboration With The @stealboyz (@chrissjamess__ & @andrejamess__ )We Will Be Releasing 4 Different Color Dyed GF-01’s In Limited Amounts Per Colorway.  The @stealboyz Process : 

Every shoe is stripped down completely. We remove all laces, insoles and hardware.

We mix the dye and setup each color for there dip. 

After air drying we carefully hand distress each shoe and then properly reconstruct it and sew it with a cross stitch it. 

Reinstall all parts to factory settings and the shoe is completed 

All 4 Releasing Next Friday July 23rd At 12 Pm Eastern On Johngeigerco.com Who Else Should We Collab With?
